      "line": 63,
      "message": "For xacml-pdp, you can't pass arguments like this.Configuration and properties file are directly specified in the script (similar to PAP). It is better to mount the etc directory with all the necessary files like defaultConfig, topic.properties and ssl so that xacml picks those up while running the script. See how this done for PAP above.\nThen you don't need this line.",
